c: 40
v: 5
t: "Abantu bakwaNûh baphika ngaphambili kunabo nabangakholwayo emva kwabo, ukanti sizwe ngasinye saba nenjongo (yokwenza iyelenqe) ngokuchasene noMthunywa waso, ngenjongo yokumhlasela, kananjalo baphikisana (ngokusebenzisa) ubuxoki (bezama) ukutshitshisa inyaniso. Ndabahlasela ke, (sabasibi) kanjani ke isohlwayo saM"